data.description: Seller will pay for Buyer Rate Buy-Down! STARLINK SATELLITE INTERNET in place and transferrable. This one is a gem! Welcome home to your own very secluded 38-acre parcel with a custom southern-style home. Hunt on your own land as it is plentiful of wild deer, turkey and quail. There is a shooting range as well as an additional cleared five-acres of land which can be used for agriculture, horses, cattle, etc. The house itself has a massive wrap-around porch for relaxing, entertaining or just enjoying the sounds of the woods. The main floor has high cathedral ceilings with a wood-paneled fireplace taking center stage. The open concept living space is flanked by windows all around for loads of natural light and beautiful views of the property. The master bedroom is also located on the first floor with the additional three bedrooms on the second floor. Don't miss out on this home!  This property is currently having a long, paved driveway installed. HVAC, Roof and Water Heater are all original (2014).
